entries.femaleVariant: Choom. Tellin' ya. You're an experiment. I'm an experiment. Pacifica's their little sandbox.
Ehh, quit talkin' out of your ass.
I mean it! Think! Pacifica, the ocean, sand... Sandbox! Human experiments!
Why you think the corpos don't just swarm in here and tear it all down? Like in North Oak, way back when.
Wrong! 'Cause they're doin' secret shit!  X-ray radiation an'... whatever the fuck! All them weird-talkin' Haitians are their spies!
Mhm. Go ahead, tell the Voodoos that. Least then I won't have to listen to your scop no more.
Fuck, just hear me out! Pacifica's their little cage, and we are the rats!
